position Software Engineer
date_joined 01/01/2020
date_exit 12/31/2023


3 tables
1 personal table 1 - addPerson()
  - name to hobbies 
2 education table 2- addEducation()
  - elementary to other skills
3 employment table
  - company to date exit - 3 - addEmployment()


3 functions
1 - addPerson()
2- addEducation()
3 - addEmployment()

